AUTH: api/auth

signup    POST  user

login     POST  user

logout    POST   message

loggedin  GET   user


PRODUCT: api/product

/         GET     all products

/         POST    create new product

/:id      DELETE  delete product

/:id      GET     retrieve product

/:id      PUT     update product


DEVICE: api/device

/         GET     all devices

/         POST    create new device

/:id      DELETE  delete device

/:id      GET     retrieve device

/:id      PUT     update device


EXTENDED device: api/device/mydevices

/         GET     all devices => registered user





